OL,5, Support for pupils who have special    
OL,6, needs is "beyond crisis" in England and
OL,7, "sucking money from budgets" for all   
OL,8, children, a report says.               
OL,10,FNearly all schools (97%) responding to 
OL,11,Fa survey by a head teachers' union said
OL,12,Fthey received insufficient funding to  
OL,13,Fsupport pupils who had special needs.  
OL,15,FThe National Association of Head       
OL,16,FTeachers says funding has to rise so   
OL,17,Fall pupils can be supported to learn.  
OL,19,FThe government said its review of the  
OL,20,Fsystem aimed to improve things.        
